{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Midnight Shift&quot;</strong> - is a first-person horror game set at a gas station in Wisconsin.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Average gameplay time: 60 minutes</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071770/extras/glitch_footage_for_free___upd_link_3.gif?t=1729857082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It was an ordinary gas station, and it seemed like nothing was happening. However, during one of the shifts, one of the employees went missing, and Alice took her place.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alice is a girl who needs money to live. That's why she agreed to work overtime. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071770/extras/2.gif?t=1729857082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you will spend a few days with the main heroine, uncover the details of a horrifying incident, and experience the full terror of working alone during midnight shifts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At first, everything seems normal: a gas station, customers, a quiet night. But as the hours pass, strange events begin to occur. Unusual customers show up at the station, their behavior raises suspicions, and inexplicable things happen around you. You\u2019ll need to react to what\u2019s happening, keep an eye on the surroundings, and make decisions that may determine not only the outcome of the night but also your survival.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3071770?t=1729857082","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3071770?t=1729857082","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st